### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user1",
  "password": "password1"
}

### Get areas
GET http://localhost:4000/api/areas

### Create booking
POST http://localhost:4000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "areaId": "A1"
}

### Get my bookings
GET http://localhost:4000/api/bookings/my/1

### Get all bookings (admin)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/bookings/all
